Output images/pixi-workflow.gif
Set Shell fish
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Hide
Type "cd $(mktemp -d)"
Enter
Type "cp ~/dev/personal_website/content/posts/transparent_metagenomics/pixi.toml ."
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show

Type "cat pixi.toml"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "pixi install"
Enter
Sleep 25s
